
VCDOM [RubyGem project]

----------------------------------------------------------------
This project makes a implementation of W3C DOM working on Ruby.
Now, it's under construction...

=== Sample ===

# ruby code

require "vcdom/xml_parser"
require "vcdom/xml_serializer"

parser = VCDOM::XMLParser.new()
input  = VCDOM::XMLInput.new()
serializer = VCDOM::XMLSerializer.new()

input.string_data = "<test>aaaa</test>"
doc = parser.parse( input )
serializer.write_to_string( doc ) 
    #=> "<test>aaa</test>"
